com.raweng.built

Class FileObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.raweng.built.FileObject

  • public class FileObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class to upload a single file with ACL and tags to built.io.
    Author:
    raw engineering, Inc

    User needs to add following entries in manifest while using download function.

  • Allows an application to write to external storage.
